name: Conflict Space Prototype.
description:
WHEN YOU DIE CLICK RESTART

Hello welcome to my prototype game that I hope to finish more in the future. In this game you will have to dodge the bullets and have to chase the ship. I want to add story line where you are leaving earth and trying to catch the aliens.

How to play: To play the game you are going to jump over the bullets. If you don't jump and the bullet hits you you will get a text " GAME OVER". To jump just click over the game.

BY:  Dead Zone
